      "text": "These predictions are an expression of our imagination, our [[Creative Imagination]]. We recognise the uncertainty of these natural phenomena and attempt to use data, formulas and tests, which create more data, to stabilise the uncertainty of the experience. We become attached to this information as a knowing and feel distressed when it is wrong."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
